This paper discusses the integration of crowdsourcing and machine inference systems, which is a topic that falls under the sub-category of Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC). The paper also discusses strategies for improving accuracy and decreasing cost, which are topics that are relevant to Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Cybersecurity (cs.CY), and Information Retrieval (cs.IR).
